-- Target says Ulrich to retire as CEO
-- 
-- Wed Jan 9, 2008 4:57pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/09/us-target-ceo-idUSWNAS604220080109

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Target Corp ( TGT.N ) said on Wednesday that Bob Ulrich will retire as the retailer's chief executive as of May 1, but will remain chairman through the end of fiscal 2008. 

 Company president Gregg Steinhafel will succeed Ulrich as chief executive, the company said. (Reporting by  Martinne Geller ; editing by Carol Bishopric)